      "text": "workflow logic:\n- first encounter of promise.race(a, b, c)\n-    queue up a 'race' span with A, B, C children\n- second encounter (when A resolves)\n-   force delete B and C off the queue\n-   resolve to A\n- (maybe) third encounter if B resolves\n-   noop\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "workflow logic:\n- first encounter of promise.race(a, b, c)\n-    queue up a 'race' span with A, B, C children\n- second encounter (when A resolves)\n-   force delete B and C off the queue\n-   resolve to A\n- (maybe) third encounter if B resolves\n-   noop\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
