      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1751925033958,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "benefit:\n* prevent queueing the message\nin the first place (use VQS idempotency\nfeature when enqueueing)",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "benefit:\n* prevent queueing the message\nin the first place (use VQS idempotency feature when enqueueing)",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
    {
      "id": "njGWb6Jx3rXzzX-RPT0Vp",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1382.1523674391728,
      "y": 484.29464389386516,
      "width": 358.6624548835121,
      "height": 54,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "ad",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1732882905,
      "version": 427,
      "versionNonce": 1163304825,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1751139741576,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "benefit: declarative - like a memoized\nfn",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "benefit: declarative - like a memoized fn",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
    {
      "id": "-pYhttxu3xdOnN7MiIOWg",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1582.1841229320526,
      "y": 615.1325519468724,
      "width": 710.4142078114639,
      "height": 459,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "ae",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 935049399,
      "version": 1990,
      "versionNonce": 811182809,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1751169076411,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "cases :\n* Idempotency scoped to a run\n   > this happens implicitly because of workflow semantics\n* idempotency scoped across a run (i.e. step referenced multiple times in a\nworkflow)\n   > just include the run ID (ex: `${ctx.runId}:${someKey}`)\n* idempotency scoped across all runs in a workflow\n   > just include the workflow name/ID (ex. `workflow1:${someKey}`)\n* global step idempotency (across all workflows)\n   > default behaviour\n\nconsiderations:\n* how do we uniquely identify the step to use for caching if the name of the\nstep will change (or as the generated name changes across\nbuilds/environments). trigger.dev requests an explicit task ID but we don't\n* on cache hit, do we throw an error or return cached value\n  > probably support both (ex: `failOnCacheHit: true`)",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "cases :\n* Idempotency scoped to a run\n   > this happens implicitly because of workflow semantics\n* idempotency scoped across a run (i.e. step referenced multiple times in a workflow)\n   > just include the run ID (ex: `${ctx.runId}:${someKey}`)\n* idempotency scoped across all runs in a workflow\n   > just include the workflow name/ID (ex. `workflow1:${someKey}`)\n* global step idempotency (across all workflows)\n   > default behaviour\n\nconsiderations:\n* how do we uniquely identify the step to use for caching if the name of the step will change (or as the generated name changes across builds/environments). trigger.dev requests an explicit task ID but we don't\n* on cache hit, do we throw an error or return cached value\n  > probably support both (ex: `failOnCacheHit: true`)",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
    {
      "id": "ZgFobCtPOmcjGrI8wVVpj",
